{"tid":1518771,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[新學期笑話] 黑警子女打電話報稱受同學仔隔離杯葛……","createTime":"2019-08-30T10:47:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T01:38:21.000Z","uid":281025,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e91c9ad40c309fa305b17dcc28357f40f26c4eb2","tid":1518771,"uid":281025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:47:22.000Z","msg":"黑警子女打電話報稱在校園受同學仔隔離杯葛，大多數老師另眼相看&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n元朗差佬李漢民話：咪串返你同學老師，話佢哋咁樣做係唔會令到我哋驚㗎！<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰話：每間學校派一隊防暴去日間駐守，護送你哋返放學，咪解決囉。<br />\n<br />\n999接線員好唔耐煩咁話：驚就唔好返學啦！<br />\n<br />\n員佐級協會主席林志偉話：曱甴仔女喳嘛，兜頭兜面噴佢哋成罐殺蟲水，咪解決囉。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊話：一日内檢控完尼班同學老師暴動罪，兩日内送上法庭審，夠阻嚇性掛～咪解決囉。<br />\n<br />\n李家超話：警方現在是「使用適當及必要的武力」對付同學老師的時候啦～鬧大左就叫警監會扮認真調查，咪解決囉。<br />\n<br />\n鄧乃強話：Call警車押送同學老師去新屋嶺&ldquo;好好招待&rdquo;，拖夠48個鐘，咪解決囉。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭話：咁後生仔冇stake㗎嘛～拉曬今次暴動相關既所有同學老師校長返差館，俾班落左嚟既&ldquo;便衣&rdquo;武警&ldquo;教育&rdquo;佢哋幾個月，咪解決囉。"},{"pid":"2d1519d514ddf15fa33246fce8b0cf2862571acf","tid":1518771,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OUQvG7y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUQvG7y.gif&h=0b84475f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUilSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=5e64b1c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUilSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=3764e464\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUilSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=c06409a1\" 